fields.name: Handcrafted Beaded Necklace
fields.description: Beautiful handcrafted beaded necklace made with semi-precious stones and sterling silver clasp. Each piece is unique with careful attention to detail.

fields.name: Wire-Wrapped Pendant Necklace
fields.description: Stunning wire-wrapped pendant necklace featuring a natural crystal. The intricate wire work showcases the beauty of the stone, creating a one-of-a-kind piece.

fields.name: Copper Leaf Earrings
fields.description: Delicate copper earrings hand-forged into beautiful leaf shapes. These lightweight earrings feature surgical steel ear wires for sensitive ears.

fields.name: Ceramic Stud Earrings Set
fields.description: Set of three pairs of ceramic stud earrings, each hand-painted with unique designs. Perfect for mixing and matching with any outfit.

fields.name: Woven Friendship Bracelet
fields.description: Handwoven friendship bracelet made with colorful embroidery thread. Each bracelet features a unique pattern that won't fade or wear away.

fields.name: Adjustable Leather Cuff
fields.description: Hand-tooled leather cuff bracelet with adjustable snap closure. Features a beautiful mandala design that is carefully pressed into the leather.

fields.name: Ceramic Speckled Mug
fields.description: Handcrafted ceramic mug with a beautiful speckled glaze. Perfect for your morning coffee or tea. Each mug is wheel-thrown and unique.

fields.name: Ceramic Travel Mug with Lid
fields.description: Handmade ceramic travel mug with silicone lid. Keeps your drinks hot while on the go. Features a comfortable handle and non-slip base.

fields.name: Ceramic Serving Bowl Set
fields.description: Set of three nested ceramic serving bowls. Perfect for salads, pasta, or serving snacks. Each bowl is hand-thrown and glazed with food-safe materials.

fields.name: Ceramic Ramen Bowl
fields.description: Large handcrafted ceramic ramen bowl. Perfect for soup, noodles, or rice dishes. Features a beautiful glazed interior with a matte exterior.

fields.name: Walnut End Grain Cutting Board
fields.description: Handcrafted end grain cutting board made from solid walnut. The end grain construction helps preserve your knife edges and provides a durable cutting surface.

fields.name: Maple and Cherry Serving Board
fields.description: Beautiful handcrafted serving board made from maple and cherry woods. Features an integrated handle and juice groove. Perfect for charcuterie or serving appetizers.

fields.name: Wooden Wall Clock
fields.description: Handcrafted wooden wall clock made from reclaimed oak. Features hand-cut numbers and a quiet sweep movement. Each clock is unique due to the natural variations in the wood.

fields.name: Wooden Desk Organizer
fields.description: Handcrafted wooden desk organizer with compartments for pens, pencils, and other office supplies. Made from solid cherry wood with a natural oil finish.

fields.name: Lavender Soy Candle
fields.description: Handmade soy wax candle with essential lavender oil. Burns cleanly for approximately 40 hours. Comes in a reusable glass container.

fields.name: Vanilla & Cinnamon Candle Set
fields.description: Set of two handmade candles with vanilla and cinnamon scents. Perfect for creating a warm, inviting atmosphere. Made with all-natural soy wax and cotton wicks.

fields.name: Goat Milk Soap Collection
fields.description: Collection of four handmade goat milk soaps in different scents: lavender, rose, eucalyptus, and unscented. Gentle on skin and naturally moisturizing.

fields.name: Exfoliating Coffee Soap
fields.description: Handmade exfoliating soap made with real coffee grounds. Helps scrub away dead skin while the caffeine helps reduce inflammation. Made with all-natural ingredients.

fields.name: Hand-Knitted Infinity Scarf
fields.description: Soft, chunky infinity scarf hand-knitted with premium merino wool. Warm and cozy for cold weather. Available in multiple colors.

fields.name: Knitted Baby Blanket
fields.description: Hand-knitted baby blanket made with super soft cotton yarn. Perfect for newborns and infants. Machine washable and durable.

fields.name: Floral Embroidery Hoop Art
fields.description: Hand-embroidered floral design in a wooden hoop. Ready to hang on your wall. Each piece is unique and made with high-quality embroidery floss.

fields.name: Embroidered Tea Towel Set
fields.description: Set of two hand-embroidered cotton tea towels with botanical designs. Practical and beautiful addition to any kitchen. Machine washable.

fields.name: Handmade Birthday Card Set
fields.description: Set of five handmade birthday cards with envelopes. Each card features a unique design with hand-stamped and embellished details.

fields.name: Watercolor Thank You Cards
fields.description: Pack of eight handmade thank you cards with hand-painted watercolor designs. Comes with matching envelopes and blank insides for your personal message.

fields.name: Leather-Bound Journal
fields.description: Handcrafted leather-bound journal with handmade paper. Features a wrap-around tie closure and 120 unlined pages perfect for sketching or writing.

fields.name: Marbled Paper Notebook
fields.description: Handmade notebook with a cover featuring original hand-marbled paper. Contains 80 pages of high-quality lined paper perfect for journaling or note-taking.
